These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: nigerian, pakistani, dutch, australian
Hobby: photography, magic-tricks, traveling, skydiving
1. Hobby:skydiving is on the left of Nationality:dutch##1
2. Nationality:nigerian is on the left of Hobby:magic-tricks##1
3. Nationality:australian is in an odd position##4
4. Hobby:traveling is on the left or right of Hobby:skydiving##3
5. Nationality:nigerian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | pakistani | australian | dutch |
| Hobby        | photography | magic-tricks   | skydiving | traveling    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Hobby: board-games, card-games, rock-climbing, dancing
Color: blue, emerald, apricot, brown
1. Hobby:card-games is on the left of Hobby:dancing##1
2. Color:blue is on the left of Color:apricot##1
3. Color:apricot is in an odd position##4
4. Color:blue == Hobby:board-games##1
5. Color:emerald is on the right of Color:apricot##1
6. Color:blue == Hobby:board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | board-games  | card-games  | dancing |
| Color   | brown    | blue | apricot | emerald    |

