2. Pet:frog is in an even position##4
3. Color:azure is on the left or right of Pet:rat##3
4. Color:azure is on the right of Color:pink##1
5. Color:chestnut is in an odd position##4
6. Pet:rat is on the right of Pet:frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Pet          | dog | frog | rat    | lizard      |
| Color   | pink        | azure     | chestnut | green |

